Zhejiang Grandwall Electric Science&Technology Co.,Ltd.
(China)
Zhejiang Grandwall Electric Science&Technology Co., Ltd. is a publicly listed company on the Shanghai Stock Exchange (stock abbreviation: Grandwall Technology, stock code: 603897). It is one of the top three manufacturers in the industry specializing in the production of electromagnetic wires. The company is headquartered in Huzhou, Zhejiang Province, located in the core area of the Yangtze River Delta, with an annual production capacity of 120,000 tons of electromagnetic wires.
The company has long been dedicated to the research and production of electromagnetic wire products, which are widely used in industries such as new energy, household appliances, industrial motors, automotive electronics, power tools, and instruments. Over the years, with strong scientific research capabilities, rigorous inspection attitude, advanced management methods, and a steady development philosophy, the company has accumulated a series of proprietary manufacturing technologies and experiences.
As the vice chairman unit of China's electromagnetic wire industry, Grandwall Technology has participated in the formulation of multiple industry product standards, effectively promoting the development of China's electromagnetic wire industry. It is a trusted long-term partner in the global electromagnetic wire application field, and has grown and expanded together with most customers, providing excellent products and efficient services.
The company actively expands the global market and strives to provide the most valuable service solutions for the electromagnetic wire application field worldwide.

Table of Contents
About Us
Liugao Power Technology Group Zhejiang Transmission and Distribution Co., Ltd. is a wholly-owned subsidiary of Liugao Power Technology Group, focusing on the overseas market development and sales of the group’s power equipment products. As an important component of Liugao Electric Power Technology Group, the company has a strong research and development, production, and sales team, as well as a comprehensive quality management system and after-sales service system.
Liugao Power Technology Group, formerly known as Shanghai Liugao Power Technology Co., Ltd., was established in 2008 and upgraded to Liugao Power Technology Group in 2016. The company is headquartered in Shanghai and has a nationwide production base and sales network. The products under the group cover the entire chain of high and low voltage power equipment, among which the main products include almost all high-voltage components such as 10KV-35KV oil immersed and dry type transformers, box type substations, complete sets of high and low voltage switchgear, outdoor and indoor vacuum circuit breakers, isolation switches, drop type fuses, etc.
Liugao Electric Power Technology Group has always been an important power equipment provider for China Southern Power Grid, participating in numerous domestic and international project projects, especially excelling in complete power solutions. The company’s products have passed the testing and certification of the most important domestic and international authoritative institutions, including ISO9001, ISO45001, ISO14001, KEMA, XIHARI&MA and other related certifications.
Liugao Power Technology Group has always adhered to the concept of “technological innovation, quality first, and service first”, continuously improving the quality of products and services, and providing customers with more high-quality products and solutions. In the future, the company will continue to be committed to the research and development and manufacturing of power equipment, providing customers with more professional, efficient, and reliable power equipment products and services, achieving a win-win situation.
